  "texts": [
    "6 The effective Hamiltonian includes the currentcurrent operators O 1,2O 1 = (c α γ µ P L b β)(s β γ µ P L c α), O 2 = (cγ µ P L b)(sγ µ P L c),(39)the QCD penguin operators O 3,...,6O 3 = (sγ µ P L b) q (qγ µ P L q), O 4 = (s α γ µ P L b β) q (q β γ µ P L q α),(40)O 5 = (sγ µ P L b) q (qγ µ P R q), O 6 = (s α γ µ P L b β) q (q β γ µ P R q α),(41)with P R,L = 1 ± γ 5 2, α,β colour indices, and the sum in ( 40)-( 41) running over the flavours q = u, d, s, c, b.",
    "The other operators in (38) are the magnetic penguin operatorsO 7 = e 16π 2 sσ µν (m s P L + m b P R) b F µν,(42)O ′ 7 = e 16π 2 sσ µν (m s P R + m b P L) b F µν,(43)O 8 = g s 16π 2 sα σ µν λ a 2 αβ (m s P L + m b P R)b β G a µν,(44)O ′ 8 = g s 16π 2 sα σ µν λ a 2 αβ (m s P R + m b P L)b β G a µν,(45)and the semileptonic electroweak penguin operatorsO 9 = e 2 16π 2 sγ µ P L b l1 γ µ ℓ 2, O ′ 9 = e 2 16π 2 sγ µ P R b l1 γ µ ℓ 2,(46)O 10 = e 2 16π 2 sγ µ P L b l1 γ µ γ 5 ℓ 2, O ′ 10 = e 2 16π 2 sγ µ P R b l1 γ µ γ 5 ℓ 2.",
    "(47)Primed operators have opposite chirality with respect to the unprimed ones.",
    "λ a are the Gell-Mann matrices, F µν and G a µν the electromagnetic and gluonic field strengths, e and g s the electromagnetic and strong coupling constant.",
    "The b and s quark mass m b and m s are defined in the MS scheme at the scale m b.In SM, at the leading order in α s the only operators to be considered are O 7 and O 9,10 with ℓ 1 = ℓ 2."
